title: Vitali's Bistro Kosher Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Kosher, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The only meat is fish; otherwise vegetarian. European style cafe offering pastries, soups, crepes, panini, wraps, veg sushi rolls, salads, bagels, omelets, fresh squeezed juices, and smoothies. Has Wi-Fi and live music some Sat nights.
